---
// ShippingSection — Formas de envío disponibles
---

<section id="envios" class="shipping-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-subtitle">🚚 Formas de Envío</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Recibe tu pedido donde quieras</h2>
    <p class="shipping-section__description">
      Llevamos tus productos a todo el país con las mejores opciones de envío. Rapidez y seguridad garantizadas.
    </p>

    <div class="shipping-section__grid">
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/>
            <polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/>
            <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/>
            <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="shipping-card__title">Envío Estándar</h3>
        <ul class="shipping-card__details">
          <li>💰 Desde $2.990</li>
          <li>📍 A todo el país</li>
          <li>🔔 Tracking incluido</li>
          <li>  Servientrega</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="shipping-card shipping-card--featured">
        <div class="shipping-card__badge">MÁS ELEGIDO</div>
        <div class="shipping-card__icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            <line x1="13" y1="2" x2="3" y2="14"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="14" x2="22" y2="14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="shipping-card__title">Envío Express</h3>
        <ul class="shipping-card__details">
          <li>⚡ 1-2 días hábiles</li>
          <li>💰 Desde $5.990</li>
          <li>📍 Capital y GBA</li>
          <li>🔔 Tracking en tiempo real</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="shipping-card__title">Retiro en Local</h3>
        <ul class="shipping-card__details">
          <li>🏪 Sin costo adicional</li>
          <li>📅 Coordinamos horario</li>
          <li>📍 CABA</li>
          <li>✅ Verificación inmediata</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="shipping-section__info">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
        <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/>
        <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/>
      </svg>
      <p><strong>Importante:</strong> Todos los envíos incluyen seguro contra daños y pérdidas. Recibí tu código de seguimiento 24h después de la compra.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .shipping-section__description {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: -1.5rem auto var(--space-2xl);
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .shipping-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .shipping-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    position: relative;
  }

  .shipping-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .shipping-card--featured {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    border-width: 2px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .shipping-card__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .shipping-card__icon-wrapper {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .shipping-card--featured .shipping-card__icon-wrapper {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  .shipping-card__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .shipping-card__details {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .shipping-card__details li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    padding: 4px 0;
  }

  .shipping-section__info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: var(--space-xl) auto 0;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .shipping-section__info svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
</style>
